Center for Language and Speech Processing </A>.

<HR>
<h3> Research Interests </h3> 

My research interests include natural language processing and 
spoken language systems, machine translation, information retrieval,
very large text databases and machine learning.

<p>
<HR>

<p> Program Chair, <b><!WA3><A HREF="http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~yarowsky/wvlc3.html">
3rd Workshop on Very Large Corpora</A></b>

<p> Secretary, <b><!WA4><A HREF="http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~yarowsky/sigdat.html">
SIGDAT</A> </b>(The ACL SIG for statistical/data-driven methods in NLP)

<p> Program committee member, <b><!WA5><A HREF="http://www.cs.jhu.edu/~brill/Conf_on_VLC.txt">
Conference on Empirical Methods in Natural Language Processing</A></b>

<p> Program committee member, <b><!WA6><A HREF="http://www.cs.columbia.edu/~radev/acl/docs/velingrad1.txt">
International Conference on Recent Advances in Natural Language Processing</A></b>

<p> Moderator, <b><!WA7><A HREF="mailto:empiricists_request@unagi.cis.upenn.edu">
Empiricists Mailing List</A></b> (focused on statistical and data-driven approaches 
to natural language processing).

